reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars La grafica es super buena
reviews.reviewText: La grafica es excelente, lo único malo es su precio pero fuera de eso es super ya que puedes jugar cualquier juego con ella en ultra a 120 fps o mas dependiendo la configuración de los gráficos, es super silenciosa y da muy buenas temperaturas. Lo probe con el avatar frontiers of pandora que venia con la tarjeta grafica y las temperaturas se quedaron en 72 o 76 grados nunca llega a 80 grados, por lo general siempre tengo una temperatura de 56 o 62 grados en los juegos pero para los mas exigentes nunca llega a 80 grados por lo cual es excelente.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Never got my starfield code. Was lied to
reviews.reviewText: GPU Is great actually. Exceeded expectations. Love XFX they're the new EVGA imo. But amazon customer service is very poor. was given the run around about my starfield code, have never gotten it. Have given up on it. Had a rep tell me that I had to have an amazon business account when purchasing the GPU to receive the code. lol Was lied to in chat support, was lied to on the phone. Overall horrible customer support from amazon. Buy this on someplace like New egg, if you buy from amazon you'll likely not get the Starfield code. And be met with rude customer service reps who get irritated at you because you can't understand their English, since it's not their first language.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars You should buy the 7800xt but this is still a great option if you can’t find one
reviews.reviewText: This card is amazing don’t get me wrong but the 7800xt is about 10% faster for only $50 more. To put that into perspective the 7900xt is only 10% faster than that and it’s $250 more. This is a great card and I bought it because I couldn’t find a 7800xt but I’m really happy with it. Make sure your case is big enough. I had to buy a new case because this card is soooooo big.

reviews.reviewText: I’ve used Linux Mint for a few years now and unfortunately this gpu did not work ootb. I switched to Kubuntu 23.10 and it worked perfectly. You might have to wait for other distros to use the latest kernel.

C'est la 2e fois que j'achète une carte RADEON et malheureusement, ça fais aussi 2 fois que j'ai des problèmes. En ce qui concerne celle-ci, la RX 7700 XT c'est en jouant à World of Warcraft que l'ordinateur à gelé, suivi d'un écran noire pendant environ 10 secondes pour ensuite revenir au bureau de Windows avec le jeux toujours ouvert mais dans la barre des tâches. Un pop up disait qu'un retart de pilotes a été détecté. J'ai donc fait les mises à jours Windows (11) et procédé à une nouvelle installation des pilotes AMD... ce qui n'a pas réglé le problème. Voici ma configuration : MB B550 Plus Prime, Ryzen R7 5800X, 32G (2x16G) @ 3200MHz Vipers, 850W Gold v2. J'ai retourné la carte.

I don’t write a lot of reviews but I think this is warranted. I would stay away from 7000k series card from AMD. There is a lot of reports of users including myself having frequent blackscreens resulting in the need to to hard reset the system. I upgraded an older computer from an RX580 with this card and I am seriously considering returning it. Buy at your own risk.
